Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:34.99,片名,,0,0,0,,{\i1\move(1270,679,642,645,0,125)\frz357.5}电波诚译
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们 你们好啊\N{\fs38}Bonjour, mes amis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有人在巴黎过得不错呀\N{\fs38}Oh, someone had a good time in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我和Kevin开心极了\N{\fs38}Oh, Kevin and I shared a perfect week together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像是躺在牛角面包上一样\N{\fs38}I feel like I'm floating on a croissant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道为什么人们不多唱唱歌呢\N{\fs38}I wonder why people don't just break into song more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都跟你申请了几个月了\N{\fs38}I've been asking you for months if I could
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能不能这样接电话\N{\fs38}answer the phone like,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管试试吧\N{\fs38}Give it a whirl, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 他说话押韵\N{\fs38}Guys, he's rhyming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还让Gina唱歌了\N{\fs38}He's telling Gina to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Holt警监在假期玩嗨了\N{\fs38}Captain Holt is on a vacation high!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说什么他都会答应的\N{\fs38}He will say yes to anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一匹警用马\N{\fs38}I would like a police horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让Terry一直骑在上面\N{\fs38}and I'd like Terry to be riding it almost constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想找个负责人力资源的来提醒下各位\N{\fs38}I'd like an HR person to remind everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫办公室规则\N{\fs38}about workplace boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种日本产的马桶圈\N{\fs38}The Japanese make toilet seats
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会射出一股温水 就射在你的\N{\fs38}which squirt a heated jet of water right up your...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停 别说下去了\N{\fs38}I'm gonna stop you right there, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要的是一辆装甲运兵车\N{\fs38}What we need in here is an armored personnel carrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辆坦克\N{\fs38}a tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两辆 我也要\N{\fs38}Two tanks. I want a tank too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 一人一辆坦克\N{\fs38}Great, so everyone gets a tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得不能坏了Holt警监的假后好心情\N{\fs38}Just remember we can't ruin Captain Holt's vacation high,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以谁都不能惹他生气\N{\fs38}so no one say anything that'll upset him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 不 那两个白痴在那干嘛\N{\fs38}Oh, no, what are those morons doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能没那么糟 也许他们没惹警监生气\N{\fs38}Maybe it's not that bad; maybe they didn't upset him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们干了什么 说了什么\N{\fs38}What'd you do? What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我们只是欢迎警监回来\N{\fs38}Nothing. We just said, "Welcome back."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一起笑了笑他新长出来的肥肉\N{\fs38}And laughed with him about all the weight he gained in France.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都站在这儿干什么\N{\fs38}Why is everyone just standing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干活去\N{\fs38}Get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 我的坦克\N{\fs38}So long, tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦克\N{\fs38}Tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在巴黎胖了三磅\N{\fs38}I gained three pounds in Paris...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三磅啊\N{\fs38}three pounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry 有你的快递\N{\fs38}Hey, Terry, I have a package for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 警长大人收到礼物了\N{\fs38}Ooh, Sarge got a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"箱子里是什么"\N{\fs38}"What's in the box?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德 皮特 "七宗罪"\N{\fs38}Brad Pitt, "Se7en."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说真的 箱子里是什么\N{\fs38}But seriously, what's in the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上最糟糕的东西\N{\fs38}The worst thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 蠢货\N{\fs38}Shut up, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁寄给你只小猫\N{\fs38}Okay, so who sent you a kitten
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你为什么这么讨厌它\N{\fs38}and why do you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一只小猫\N{\fs38}It's not a kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在扇我的脸啊\N{\fs38}It's a slap in the face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为二十年前的某件事\N{\fs38}for something that happened 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:01:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你还是平顶头的时候吗\N{\fs38}When you had a flat top?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你剪过平顶头\N{\fs38}I know you had a flat top,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为见过照片\N{\fs38}'cause I saw pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 继续吧 平顶头Terry\N{\fs38}Sorry, go on with your story, Flat Top Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是1995年\N{\fs38}It was 1995.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚成为警探\N{\fs38}I'd just made detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一天去6-5区的时候特别兴奋\N{\fs38}I was really excited about my first day at the 6-5,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但警队里都是一群混蛋\N{\fs38}but the guys in the squad were a bunch of jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 我是Terry\N{\fs38}Hi, I'm Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的办公桌在哪呀\N{\fs38}Which desk is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破个案子\N{\fs38}Solve a case,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就有办公桌了\N{\fs38}then you get a desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样的事还有很多\N{\fs38}They were like that about a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破个案子 你才有咖啡喝\N{\fs38}Whoa, solve a case, then you get coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破个案子 你才能在给Debbie的生日卡上签名\N{\fs38}Solve a case, then you can sign Debbie's birthday card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来你似乎得破个案子\N{\fs38}Sounds like you needed to solve a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样 所以我选了个最难的\N{\fs38}Exactly, so I picked the biggest one I could find:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起连环入室盗窃案 全都是一样的作案手法\N{\fs38}a string of B&Es,all with the same M.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案犯从高层建筑的窗户爬进去\N{\fs38}Guy climbed in through high-rise windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个月之后 我发现了嫌犯\N{\fs38}After a month, I found my suspect:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dmitri Kuzkho\N{\fs38}Dmitri Kuzkho.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有犯罪记录的前杂技演员\N{\fs38}Ex-acrobat with a criminal record.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马戏团人渣 一定是他\N{\fs38}Circus trash! It has to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么说的\N{\fs38}That's exactly what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马戏团人渣 一定是他\N{\fs38}Circus trash! It has to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我追查那个杂技演员\N{\fs38}I tracked down my acrobat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让特警包围他住的地方\N{\fs38}got SWAT to surround his building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都完美极了\N{\fs38}There was no way anything could go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约警察局 趴下\N{\fs38}NYPD! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴到地上\N{\fs38}Get on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来\N{\fs38}Let's see your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊噢\N{\fs38}Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙两年前从高空秋千上摔了下来\N{\fs38}My guy had a terrible trapeze fall two years prior...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的脊椎被摔成了两半\N{\fs38}snapped his spine in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这跟小猫有什么关系\N{\fs38}So why the kitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种情况下\N{\fs38}Well, in the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时可能有点慌乱\N{\fs38}I may have gotten a little flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 他养了只猫\N{\fs38}Look, he's got a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定是把猫训练成盗窃犯\N{\fs38}He trained the cat to do the robberies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以人们都叫他们"毛"贼\N{\fs38}That's why they call them cat burglars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么没人说话\N{\fs38}Why is no one saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 Terry\N{\fs38}Oh, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们寄只猫给我是为了提醒我那件事 顺便打我的脸\N{\fs38}Yeah, now they send me cats to remind me of that day and rub it in my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得在网上登个广告\N{\fs38}I'm gonna go put a ad online
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找人收养这个可恶的小粪球\N{\fs38}so I can find someone to adopt this evil, little turd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对比一下的话\N{\fs38}Counterpoint:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两只看起来还挺可爱的\N{\fs38}you two make an adorable couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建议把它放到杯子里\N{\fs38}Might I suggest putting him in a mug
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后装作要喝一口的样子\N{\fs38}and pretending to take a sip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry你这么急着走是要照我说的做吗\N{\fs38}Terry, are you stomping off to do my thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我用用你的手机吗\N{\fs38}Oh, hey, can I borrow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Genevieve去外地了\N{\fs38}Genevieve's out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要两个手机 一个发"前面" 一个发"后面"\N{\fs38}I need two phones so I can send her a "Frontie" And a "Backie."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想看见你的屁股出现在我的云相册里\N{\fs38}I don't want your ass in my cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Adrian 你住在休息室吗\N{\fs38}Adrian, are you living in the break room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没啊 怎么这么问\N{\fs38}No, why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你在我们吃饭的桌子旁 给肩膀除毛\N{\fs38}Uh, because you're shaving your shoulder in our communal eating space;
