Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是比你们伟大得多的东西的一部分\N{\fs38}You're a part of something much bigger than yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 Linetti\N{\fs38}Well, good morning, Linetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天晚上睡得像个婴儿\N{\fs38}Whoo, I slept like a frickin' baby last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在Chuck家简直像做梦\N{\fs38}Staying at Chuck's is like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小个子就爱宠着我\N{\fs38}Little guy loves doting on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你还得去买些大点的内裤\N{\fs38}although you're gonna need to buy some bigger underwear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一我们要分着穿呢\N{\fs38}if we're gonna be sharing, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我去买\N{\fs38}Okay, I'll get right on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 拿着\N{\fs38}Okay, cool. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我看着点 好么\N{\fs38}Take care of this for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿些糖当早饭\N{\fs38}I'm gonna go get some breakfast candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 过会儿见\N{\fs38}Okay, catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你和你新室友处得\N{\fs38}So things are going really good
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺不错啊 看上去\N{\fs38}with the new roomie, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了\N{\fs38}It's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴室里到处都是不知道是谁的血\N{\fs38}There's someone's blood all over the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他梦里掐了我的脖子两回\N{\fs38}He sleep-choked me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟的是 今天早上\N{\fs38}And the worst part... this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他吃光了我的麦片\N{\fs38}he ate all of my cereal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最糟的\N{\fs38}That's the worst part?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是Nortfluskers牌的麦圈\N{\fs38}They were Nortfluskers bran circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从奥斯陆海运来的\N{\fs38}I had them shipped from Oslo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我真希望他滚蛋\N{\fs38}Oh, I want him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我太害怕了不敢告诉他\N{\fs38}But I'm too scared to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 听着\N{\fs38}All right, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的精神动物\N{\fs38}I know that your spirit animal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只被踩扁了的毛虫\N{\fs38}is a caterpillar that's been stepped on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我的是匹强大的狼\N{\fs38}But mine is the mighty wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想打败狼王\N{\fs38}And if you want to beat an alpha,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就得先做狼王\N{\fs38}you have to be an alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对哦\N{\fs38}Wrongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果当受气包当的好\N{\fs38}If you're good enough at being a beta,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那狼王就会可怜你\N{\fs38}then the alpha takes mercy on you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后对你百依百顺\N{\fs38}and ends up giving you what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Boyle  - 啊\N{\fs38}- Boyle. - Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能别进你家厨房48小时左右么\N{\fs38}Could you stay out of your kitchen for the next, like, 48 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给我猎到的那只鹿剥皮\N{\fs38}I'm gonna be skinning a deer that I shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥玩意\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 再搭点塑料布\N{\fs38}Ooh, and put up some of those plastic sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本不知道我在干嘛\N{\fs38}I have no idea what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 行 真棒\N{\fs38}- Okay. - Okay, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 聊得真开心 兄弟  - 是啊\N{\fs38}- Good talk, buddy. - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿到档案了\N{\fs38}I got the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 做得好 怎么办到的\N{\fs38}Oh, nice work. How'd you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\fs38}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管档案室的警长是位女士\N{\fs38}the sergeant in charge of the file room was a lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我启动了Peralta的魅惑\N{\fs38}so I just turned on the old Peralta charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fs38}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在男厕所吐了\N{\fs38}Some dude yarfed in the men's restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能找人去清理一下么\N{\fs38}Could you please find somebody to clean that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry 根本没人吐\N{\fs38}Terry, there was no yarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我想到了\N{\fs38}Yeah, I figured that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好吧\N{\fs38}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我们拿到了什么\N{\fs38}Let's see what we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40张你站在轮椅男和他的猫旁边的照片\N{\fs38}40 photos of you standing next to the guy in the wheelchair and his cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们拍了一堆照 还做成了鼠标垫\N{\fs38}They did a photoshoot. They made mouse pads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮坏银\N{\fs38}They are bad dudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我们这样\N{\fs38}All right, here's our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去重访这案子的原始受害人\N{\fs38}We are gonna re-interview all the original victims
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从第一个开始\N{\fs38}of this case, starting with the first one,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Janice McMinnion\N{\fs38}Janice McMinnion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额 \N{\fs38}Uh....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她12年前就死了\N{\fs38}she died 12 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就第二个\N{\fs38}All right, the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也死了\N{\fs38}Also dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 干嘛不直接跳到\N{\fs38}Okay, why don't you just skip on down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个没死的人呢\N{\fs38}to the first person that's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八个\N{\fs38}Number eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八个 活着哦\N{\fs38}Number eight, way to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八个 还活着\N{\fs38}Number eight, still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 第八个 还活着  - 第八个 还活着\N{\fs38}- Number eight, still alive. - Number eight, still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先为前七个默哀\N{\fs38}Moment of silence for the first seven, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 出发\N{\fs38}All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有水银开关的压力炸弹\N{\fs38}Ah, pressure bombs with mercury switches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手机做雷管的简易爆炸装置\N{\fs38}IEDs with cell phone detonators.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这是C4么\N{\fs38}Oh, is that C4?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦天 我们今天有些很厉害的炸弹哦\N{\fs38}Oh, my, we've got some great bombs today, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fs38}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这堂课上 我们会学习怎样处置\N{\fs38}In this course, we'll be going over how to dispose
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10种不同的爆炸装置\N{\fs38}of 10 different types of explosive devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天所学能救了你和无数人的命\N{\fs38}What you learn today could save your lives and countless others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题么\N{\fs38}Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有排名或者计分系统来看出谁最棒吗\N{\fs38}Yes, Will there be a grading or point system to see who's best?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在救人方面\N{\fs38}At saving lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 在救人方面\N{\fs38}Yes, at saving lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指的就是救人啦\N{\fs38}Saving lives was always implied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会被计时\N{\fs38}Well, you will be timed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 完美  - 那就行\N{\fs38}- Perfect. - That'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我建议忽视时间 专注在\N{\fs38}But I would recommend ignoring the clock and focusing on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 是 你回答完问题了\N{\fs38}Yeah, yeah, yeah, you answered the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度点教我们\N{\fs38}Hurry up and teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 老人家\N{\fs38}Hey, Slowpoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我们出去\N{\fs38}When we get out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给你绣个枕头上面写着"打脸"\N{\fs38}I'm gonna needlepoint you a pillow that says, "Kapow."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Amy 你很烂\N{\fs38}Hey, Amy. You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是么 你猜怎么着\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah? Well, guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枕头上还有很多地方\N{\fs38}There's more room on that pillow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长话短说 你还是烂\N{\fs38}Real quick, before you finish: you still suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这场废话里我比你动脑筋得多\N{\fs38}I'm working so much harder than you on this trash talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却是受伤的那个\N{\fs38}and I'm the one whose feelings are getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Santiago Diaz 够了\N{\fs38}Santiago, Diaz... enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点不在你们俩谁最快\N{\fs38}This is not about who's fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是拆弹课堂\N{\fs38}This is a bomb dismantling class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是警员 不是在公园里下快棋的流浪儿\N{\fs38}We are police officers, not street urchins playing speed chess in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可耻啊\N{\fs38}For shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 谢谢\N{\fs38}All right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 这是Esther记得的\N{\fs38}Okay, here's what Esther remembers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被盗的那晚发生的事\N{\fs38}about the night that she was robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要么在饭店\N{\fs38}She was either at a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么在电影院 要么在做别的\N{\fs38}or the movies or doing something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要么是一个人 要么就和别人在一块\N{\fs38}And she was either alone or with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她唯一确定的事是\N{\fs38}The only thing she was absolutely sure of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着像个好人\N{\fs38}is that I seem like a very nice boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和案子无关\N{\fs38}which is not relevant to the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但让我觉得开心\N{\fs38}but did make me feel very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太傻了\N{\fs38}This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了20年\N{\fs38}It was 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人记得任何事\N{\fs38}No one remembers anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始觉得也许我们该\N{\fs38}I'm beginning to think maybe we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上那个窗台\N{\fs38}Climb out on that ledge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看罪犯是怎么进来的\N{\fs38}and see how the perp got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我想说放弃  - 什么\N{\fs38}- I was gonna say give up. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到这么惊艳的主意之后你还想放弃 Terry\N{\fs38}Right after I came up with that incredible ledge thing, Terry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在十楼 你受得了吗\N{\fs38}We're 10 stories up. You can handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长 我不怕高 好么\N{\fs38}Sarge, I'm not scared of heights, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕蜜蜂 我怕蛇\N{\fs38}I'm scared of bees, I'm scared of snakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕尼克斯队再也无法崛起\N{\fs38}and I'm scared that the Knicks might never be good again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不怕高\N{\fs38}but I am not scared of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要死了 我们要死了\N{\fs38}We're gonna die! We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要死了 我们要死了\N{\fs38}We're gonna die! We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要死了 我们要死了\N{\fs38}We're gonna die! We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要死了\N{\fs38}We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感激你一辈子 如果你不告诉别人\N{\fs38}I would appreciate it if you didn't tell anyone
