Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry 我们能破掉的 好么\N{\fs38}Terry, we are gonna solve this, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 可能我们今天做的一切工作\N{\fs38}Sure, maybe none of the work we did today
