Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jake\N{\fs38}Jake...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 绝大多数案件都在\N{\fs38}And sure, most crimes are solved
