Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1996年检查这个电梯的人叫Zerb Gudanya\N{\fs38}The guy who inspected this elevator in 1996 was named Zerb Gudanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天去的\N{\fs38}That's the same weird name
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四座大楼里所有电梯的检查员都叫这个怪名\N{\fs38}who inspected the elevators in all four of the buildings we've been to today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs38}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry 有方向了\N{\fs38}Terry, that's a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有方向了\N{\fs38}We have a lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有方向了\N{\fs38}We got a lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有方向了\N{\fs38}We got a lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要破案了\N{\fs38}We're gonna solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要破案了\N{\fs38}We're gonna solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去趟厕所\N{\fs38}I have to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去趟厕所\N{\fs38}I got to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不用  我只是沉浸在这个节奏里\N{\fs38}I actually don't; I just got in the rhythm of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是Zerb Gudanya\N{\fs38}There's Zerb Gudanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对一个电梯检查员来说这车也太奢侈了\N{\fs38}Pretty fancy car for an elevator inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俱乐部国际布莱顿海滩国际俱乐部\N{\fs38}The Club International of Brighton Beach International Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"国际"和"俱乐部"都在出现了两次\N{\fs38}"International" And "Club" Are both in the name twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry 这地方很低级\N{\fs38}Terry, this place sleazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两项前科 超出常理的富有\N{\fs38}Two priors, wealth beyond his means,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能通过电梯井接近那些公寓\N{\fs38}and he had access to the apartments through the elevator shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定是我们要找的人 出发\N{\fs38}He has to be our guy. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我会说我是Ilya 一个来自莫斯科的商人\N{\fs38}Okay, I'll say that I'm a businessman from Moscow named Ilya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卖雪地靴赚了几百万\N{\fs38}"I make millions from selling snow boots."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想显摆下口音\N{\fs38}That was more just to show off the accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是对雪地靴有特殊癖好呢\N{\fs38}I'm not wedded to the snow boots thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小伙子\N{\fs38}Hey, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不会真的以为自己可以在6-5区搞小动作\N{\fs38}You didn't really think that you could run an operation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不被我们发现吧\N{\fs38}in the 6-5 without us finding out, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没人吐了\N{\fs38}There was no yarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人好厉害\N{\fs38}This guy's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jake 这是我以前警队的同事 Holderton\N{\fs38}Jake, this is Holderton from my old precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底在找什么\N{\fs38}So who are you guys looking for in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎斑猫\N{\fs38}A Tabby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是暹罗猫\N{\fs38}Siamese?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我从没说过那只猫是盗窃犯\N{\fs38}First of all, I never said the cat was a burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是它有可能是帮凶\N{\fs38}I said he might be an accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\fs38}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真希望那个人是只猫\N{\fs38}I hope the guy in there is a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就能让你好看了\N{\fs38}That'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 他是只猫就好抓多了\N{\fs38}Yeah, if he was a cat, he'd be much easier to apprehend
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且估计也没什么危险了\N{\fs38}and probably much less dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是这么想的 走吧\N{\fs38}That's what we think. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放弃了 我需要你的帮助\N{\fs38}Okay, I give up. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要试试你的方法\N{\fs38}I'm ready to try it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来得正是时候\N{\fs38}Shh, you came at the perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在吃东西 动物吃东西的时候\N{\fs38}He's eating, and when an animal eats,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是它们最没有防备的时候\N{\fs38}that's when they're at their most vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要走过去\N{\fs38}You need to get in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他知道谁才是狼王\N{\fs38}show him who the alpha is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我需要起个狼的名字  - 好嘞\N{\fs38}- I need a wolf name. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}Virginia Woolf 是位英国女作家 意识流文学代表人物 她的姓woolf与狼wolf发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Virginia Woolf  - 啥\N{\fs38}- Virginia Woolf. - Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要当她那个人渣丈夫Leonard\N{\fs38}Well, I'm not gonna be her lame husband, Leonard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了 Virginia\N{\fs38}Okay, it's time, Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小兔崽子 咱们来谈谈\N{\fs38}Hey, little man, let's talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算在我那儿呆多久吧\N{\fs38}how much longer you're gonna stay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在威胁我吗 Chuck\N{\fs38}Are you threatening me, Chuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢不敢 长官\N{\fs38}No, I'm not, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想表达一下我有多欢迎你和我住一块儿\N{\fs38}I just want to tell you how welcome you are to stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远永远永远\N{\fs38}forever and ever and ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊敬的大人\N{\fs38}m'lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 好了\N{\fs38}Ha! Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 谢了\N{\fs38}Good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次别搞得神神叨叨的\N{\fs38}Next time don't be so weird about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所愿 祝好 长官\N{\fs38}As you wish. Good day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是很诡异\N{\fs38}That's still weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 抱歉\N{\fs38}Hey，sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:14:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一点也不烂\N{\fs38}You don't suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很抱歉\N{\fs38}I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我俩都说了伤感情的话\N{\fs38}We both said hurtful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没说 我好得很\N{\fs38}You didn't. I was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再自欺欺人了\N{\fs38}Well, now you're just lying to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Holt说得对\N{\fs38}But Holt was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该更严肃地对待这件事的\N{\fs38}We should have taken this more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定\N{\fs38}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整整好两分钟 今日最快\N{\fs38}Fastest time today by a full two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 我的妈呀\N{\fs38}Whoo, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边一切都还好吗\N{\fs38}Is everything okay over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的不能再好了\N{\fs38}Yes, couldn't be better,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我打败了这俩货\N{\fs38}because I destroyed you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼\N{\fs38}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说输赢不重要吗\N{\fs38}I thought you said this wasn't about winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么说 是为了让你们做得慢一点\N{\fs38}I did say that, so you would go slower
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就能赢了 也就是现在的结果\N{\fs38}and I would win, which is what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我们一样好胜\N{\fs38}You're just as competitive as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡扯 我比你们更好胜\N{\fs38}Absurd. I'm more competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在谁 "屌炸"了\N{\fs38}Now who's "Da bomb"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么当上警长的\N{\fs38}So what did they make you a sergeant for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮了个松果吗\N{\fs38}Did you arrest a pine cone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他过了笔试\N{\fs38}He passed a written test,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和别的警长一样\N{\fs38}just like every other sergeant did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你清楚得很\N{\fs38}You knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没啊 我在想他可能\N{\fs38}Oh, no, I thought he might have gotten
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为逮了个松果\N{\fs38}some kind of special promotion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而得到了特殊升职\N{\fs38}from busting a pine cone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛老提松果\N{\fs38}Why do you keep bringing up pine cones?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不搭边儿\N{\fs38}That's never been a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂个毛\N{\fs38}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着打脸吧\N{\fs38}You're gonna eat your words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为警长就要把这案子破了\N{\fs38}because Sarge is about to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个案子 旧案还是松果那个\N{\fs38}What, the old case or the pine cone one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上你的嘴\N{\fs38}You need to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 我们要找的人Zerb就坐那儿\N{\fs38}Look, our man Zerb is sitting right over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 他和所有的盗窃案都有关联\N{\fs38}and yeah, he's connected to all of the robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他异常可疑\N{\fs38}And he's shady as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs38}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服务员给了他一个暗号\N{\fs38}Waiter just gave him a covert signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他站起来了\N{\fs38}Now he's getting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟着那名服务员\N{\fs38}Yeah, and now he's following said waiter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下一个很可能是更可疑的地点\N{\fs38}to a secondary, most likely even shadier spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大事要发生了\N{\fs38}Something's going on in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦  - 没错了\N{\fs38}- Huh. - Yeah, right... huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快 把他抓起来  - 快来\N{\fs38}- Come on, let's go bust him! - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下  趴下\N{\fs38}Down, down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约警察\N{\fs38}NYPD!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\fs38}Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么\N{\fs38}What are you doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我胆固醇高\N{\fs38}Nothing! I have high cholesterol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老婆说我不能吃红肉\N{\fs38}My wife says I cannot have red meat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们就偷偷把炖牛肉给我\N{\fs38}so they sneak in my beef stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 别开枪\N{\fs38}Please don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了\N{\fs38}It happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这次这家伙是坐在马桶上\N{\fs38}Only this guy's sitting on a toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是轮椅上\N{\fs38}instead of a wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更蠢了\N{\fs38}That's even more dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来 过来 Terry\N{\fs38}Here, here, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近点才能把你照进去\N{\fs38}Move in closer so I can get you in the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 Jake\N{\fs38}What up, Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些崽子怎么从笼子里放出来了\N{\fs38}Why are these dicks out of their cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一夜没睡\N{\fs38}I stayed up all night
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的案子\N{\fs38}working on your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hans John和Nakatomi\N{\fs38}and Hans, John, and Nakatomi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直陪着我\N{\fs38}made for great company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给他们起的都是<虎胆龙威>里的名字\N{\fs38}I gave them all "Die Hard" Names.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搞不懂你为什么\N{\fs38}I don't understand why you wasted another night
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在这种解不开的案子上浪费一晚\N{\fs38}on a case no one's ever gonna solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长 我这会儿太困了\N{\fs38}Sarge, I am way too sleep-deprived
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法抵抗你的消极态度\N{\fs38}to deal with your negativity right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你展示一下我的成果吧\N{\fs38}Let me show you what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我首先画了个布鲁克林1996年以来\N{\fs38}I started off by making a map
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的入室盗窃案的地图\N{\fs38}of all of the burglaries that have gone down in Brooklyn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看有没有规律\N{\fs38}since 1996 to see if there was a pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我发现了这个\N{\fs38}That led me to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约犯罪太多\N{\fs38}There is so much crime in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不该住人\N{\fs38}No one should live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 我在这问题上纠结了好几个小时\N{\fs38}Anyways, I tripped out on that for a couple hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是给在我连帽衫里\N{\fs38}but I got cheered up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩耍的小猫咪拍了张照后\N{\fs38}after I took a picture of the kitties
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又精神焕发了\N{\fs38}messing around in my little hoodie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会儿给你看\N{\fs38}I'll show it to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以基本上 一晚上都浪费了\N{\fs38}So basically, you wasted a whole night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有没有 \N{\fs38}No, no, no, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦 因为然后我又埋头看你的资料了\N{\fs38}No, no, no, 'cause then I dove back into your file
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还发现了这个\N{\fs38}and found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 我人生的最低谷\N{\fs38}Cool, the low point of my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长 这张照片是1996年拍的\N{\fs38}Sarge, this photo was taken in 1996.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉我你要找的人两年前\N{\fs38}You told me your guy broke his spine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摔断了脊椎骨 也就是1994年\N{\fs38}two years before that, so '94.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看他的运动鞋\N{\fs38}Check out his sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,95年的乔丹款\N{\fs38}'95 Jordans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在事故后一年才出的\N{\fs38}They came out a year after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看鞋底\N{\fs38}Look at the soles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是泥\N{\fs38}They're all muddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说\N{\fs38}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那贱人能走\N{\fs38}That son of a bitch can walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 正解  - 走吧\N{\fs38}- Bingo. - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 猫咪小分队 集合\N{\fs38}All right. Cat squad, assemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 把猫留这儿  - 好的\N{\fs38}- Leave the cats. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Santiago Diaz 我想和你们\N{\fs38}Santiago, Diaz, I wanted to talk to you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈谈大家昨天在拆弹课程上的表现\N{\fs38}about our performance in yesterday's bomb defusing course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道了 长官 你赢了\N{\fs38}We know, sir. You won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们三个都没过\N{\fs38}No, the three of us all failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显指导员认为\N{\fs38}Apparently our instructor felt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对待课程不够严肃\N{\fs38}we didn't take it seriously enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Hitchcock和Scully过了\N{\fs38}But Hitchcock and Scully passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么可能拆得比我们好\N{\fs38}How did they defuse bombs better than we did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那些是炸弹  - 难以置信\N{\fs38}- Those were bombs? - Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们三个人的低谷\N{\fs38}It's a low moment for us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想教训就是我们不该\N{\fs38}I think the lesson here is that we should not allow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让自己的好胜心影响工作之神圣\N{\fs38}our competitiveness to interfere with the sanctity of our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全同意 长官\N{\fs38}Totally agree, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过\N{\fs38}However,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周末还有一堂精准驾驶课\N{\fs38}there is a precision driving class next weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 最快完成的人赢  - 就这么定了\N{\fs38}- Fastest one around the track wins. - It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把你们逼出路线逼到撞墙\N{\fs38}I'm gonna run you both off the road into a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会干掉你们\N{\fs38}I'm gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs38}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Chuck\N{\fs38}Hey, Chuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我把这些拿去干洗吗\N{\fs38}Will you bring these to the dry cleaner for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉干洗店红印是血 棕色的印子是\N{\fs38}Tell them the red stains are blood and the brown stains are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是血吧\N{\fs38}uh, let's say blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fs38}Well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不劳烦你装在袋子里了\N{\fs38}Don't even bother putting them in a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就用胳膊夹着吧\N{\fs38}I'll just carry them in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs38}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:18:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大胡子\N{\fs38}Beard-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天该从Charles家搬出来了\N{\fs38}It's time for you to get out of Charles's house today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 女士\N{\fs38}Hang on, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没资格叫我做事\N{\fs38}You don't tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你就错了 小姑娘\N{\fs38}Uh, that's where you're wrong, baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这片区归我管\N{\fs38}I run this precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧好了 Scully\N{\fs38}Watch this. Scully!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 给我睡觉  - 好的\N{\fs38}- Go to sleep. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你能吓唬我\N{\fs38}You think you can intimidate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当卧底的时候 "屠夫"Jimmy\N{\fs38}When I was undercover, Jimmy "The Butcher"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用园艺剪把我的小脚趾剪了\N{\fs38}cut off my little toe with garden shears
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还让我吃了 以示忠诚\N{\fs38}and made me eat it as a loyalty test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是经历过地狱的人\N{\fs38}I've been through hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么了不起的\N{\fs38}Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在商场里的太阳镜柜台做了四年\N{\fs38}I worked an a sunglass kiosk at the mall for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不仅经历过地狱\N{\fs38}So not only have I been through hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在地狱当过副经理\N{\fs38}I was assistant manager there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs38}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得从Chuckie家搬出来\N{\fs38}You're gonna get out of Chuckie's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此外\N{\fs38}And what's more,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要把住一晚的钱给他\N{\fs38}you're gonna pay him rent for the night you spent there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 还有一件事 宝贝儿\N{\fs38}- Fine. - One more thing, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在就谢谢我们两个\N{\fs38}You're gonna thank us both right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你  - 不客气\N{\fs38}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fs38}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 太厉害了  - 我就跟你说吧\N{\fs38}- That was amazing. - Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得像狼王一样镇住他\N{\fs38}He just needed to be alpha'd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说我太受气了让你看不过去 来保护我\N{\fs38}Is that what happened, or did I just beta you into protecting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是\N{\fs38}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的\N{\fs38}That's not what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你赢了\N{\fs38}This is not your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs38}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fs38}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我吗\N{\fs38}Remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好诡异\N{\fs38}So this is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑 你个马戏团人渣\N{\fs38}Oh, no, you don't, circus trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道\N{\fs38}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都能走\N{\fs38}You could walk the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫也是帮凶 对不对\N{\fs38}I was right about the cat accomplice too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫呢\N{\fs38}Now where's the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都20年了 警长 猫可能死了\N{\fs38}Been 20 years, Sarge. Cat's probably dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也得抓住它\N{\fs38}I'm still bringing him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长 你成功了\N{\fs38}Well, Sarge, you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我们要怎么\N{\fs38}Now how should we rub your sweet victory
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羞辱6-5区的蠢货呢\N{\fs38}in the 6-5's dumb faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送他们一箱老鼠\N{\fs38}We could send them a box of rats,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们就是老鼠\N{\fs38}'cause they're rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者往他们车上扔水气球\N{\fs38}Or we could drop water balloons on their cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说\N{\fs38}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\fs38}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们不该这么做\N{\fs38}I don't think we should do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定吗 全都不做吗\N{\fs38}Really? Any of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你为我做了这么多\N{\fs38}Yeah, after everything you did for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓励我\N{\fs38}encouraging me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算吓哭了\N{\fs38}going out on that ledge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也爬上了窗台\N{\fs38}even though you were scared to tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时上面有空调\N{\fs38}There was an air conditioner above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水滴到我眼睛里了\N{\fs38}It was dripping water on my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好不提了\N{\fs38}We've been over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了破案整夜没睡\N{\fs38}You stayed up all night to solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我想起 我的生命中是有人关心着我的\N{\fs38}It just reminded me that I have people in my life who cared about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么我要花这么多时间\N{\fs38}I don't know why I'm spending so much time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向不关心我的人证明什么\N{\fs38}trying to prove things to people who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在各种意义上都是一个"大"人\N{\fs38}I guess you're a big man in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本该想到的 但是 没有\N{\fs38}Which I probably should have anticipated. But, did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你干什么了 Jake  - 老鼠 我送了老鼠\N{\fs38}- What'd you do, Jake? - Rats... I did the rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等不了了\N{\fs38}I couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好和老鼠玩吧 你们这群老鼠\N{\fs38}Enjoy the rats, you rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 糟了 有一只跑到我这儿来了\N{\fs38}Hahaha. Oh, no, one's coming for me!
